博小號里點讚過內涵隊友的微博，還關注了自己的一些「惡臭粉絲」。據該網友爆料，宋雨琦的小號內容已經被自己清空了，但是她的關注和一些點讚內容還是能被大家所看到的。"},{"pid":"ca10f05958342b37549320acf8a85f07c34d350d","tid":1182852,"uid":143093,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"網民解釋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfV3iaS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfV3iaS.png&h=e0c3998b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e360113deab8c2c24ed4a8ca46bb3ffb6cb2cc1","tid":1182852,"uid":62167,"like":204,"dislike":0,"score":204,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"以上所有人，一個都唔識"},{"pid":"996aaac3d88b90dab8a0f9b55fbad7686e2d3508","tid":1182852,"uid":182615,"like":72,"dislike":2,"score":70,"quote":{"pid":"ca10f05958342b37549320acf8a85f07c34d350d","tid":1182852,"uid":143093,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"網民解釋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfV3iaS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfV3iaS.png&h=e0c3998b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZiPYcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZiPYcO.jpg&h=e8f283fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個acc係佢既?<br />\n見鏡頭面前同CLC攬頭攬頸好FREIND<br />\n背後....."},{"pid":"ba2d9e2afea7494e16260446dac2deecf5b3efc5","tid":1182852,"uid":74065,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"就咁一堆圖 睇得好辛苦"},{"pid":"51dce2bbb5620c074e20c09e63f69ca8713b6308","tid":1182852,"uid":46435,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:17:10.000Z","msg":"有無懶人包.."},{"pid":"f9455a5e58f6b3b9e5b549bf0eb56984b037d204","tid":1182852,"uid":555,"like":19,"dislike":10,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"On9先信"},{"pid":"0c670d8013ada163217abff30499077033402184","tid":1182852,"uid":205928,"like":4,"dislike":28,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"996aaac3d88b90dab